
# how to check dom0 Memory in Xenserver
/opt/xensource/libexec/xen-cmdline --get-xen dom0_mem

# how to set dom0 menory in Xenserver-

/opt/xensource/libexec/xen-cmdline --set-xen dom0_mem=<nn>M,max:<nn>M
exute above command on node by mention desire memory
For exmple you want you to set dom0 memory as 8gb then enter below command

/opt/xensource/libexec/xen-cmdline --set-xen dom0_mem=8192M,max:8192M
